### Get My Profile
GET http://localhost:5002/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update My Profile
PUT http://localhost:5002/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated Name",
  "bio": "This is my updated bio",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

###

### Get User Profile by ID
GET http://localhost:5002/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search Users
GET http://localhost:5002/users/search?q=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Search Users with Pagination
GET http://localhost:5002/users/search?q=user&skip=0&take=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create User Profile (Internal)
POST http://localhost:5002/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "displayName": "New User",
  "bio": "A new user profile"
}

###
